如果把前端框架名理解为Java后端开发：

  | 前端                   | 类比 Java 后端 | 工程文件                                     | 主要关键字                                          |
  |-----------------------|----------------|------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------------------------|
  | JavaScript/TypeScript | Java 语言        | *.ts, *.tsx, tsconfig.json               | interface, type, : string, <T>                       |
  | React                 | Spring MVC     | src/pages/*.tsx, src/components/*.tsx    | useState, useEffect, <Component />, props             |
  | Vue                   | Spring MVC     | *.vue, src/views/, src/components/       | <template>, <script setup>, ref(), v-if, v-for, @click |
  | Vite                  | Maven/Gradle   | vite.config.ts, index.html(根目录)          | defineConfig, import.meta.env                      |
  | npm/pnpm              | Maven 依赖管理     | package.json, package-lock.json          | dependencies, devDependencies, scripts            |
  | yarn                  | Maven 依赖管理     | package.json, yarn.lock                  | yarn add, yarn dev, yarn build                    |
  | node_modules          | .m2/repository | node_modules/ 目录                         | （不直接编辑，自动生成）                              |
  | package.json          | pom.xml        | package.json                             | "name", "version", "dependencies"                     |
  | recharts              | ECharts-java   | src/components/*Chart.tsx                | <LineChart>, <BarChart>, dataKey, ResponsiveContainer |
  | shadcn/ui             | UI 组件 jar      | src/components/ui/*.tsx, components.json | <Button>, <Card>, <Dialog>, @/components/ui/        |
  | Tailwind CSS          | （CSS框架）        | tailwind.config.js, globals.css          | className="flex", bg-white, text-sm, p-4           |

MCP：
spec-workflow
自测不好用，即便付出了大量token，也失意，也瞎搞

shadCN
npx shadcn@latest mcp init --client claude

列出所有registry
再网上搜索仓库并把他们添加导mcp中
npm create vite@latest netob-app -- --template react-ts
npm install -D tailwindcss@^3 postcss autoprefixer
npm install vite@^5.4.10 @vitejs/plugin-react@^4.3.3 --save-dev

vim tailwind.config.js
/** @type {import('tailwindcss').Config} */
export default {
  content: [
    "./index.html",
    "./src/**/*.{js,ts,jsx,tsx}",
  ],
  theme: {
    extend: {},
  },
  plugins: [],
}

npx tailwindcss init -p

"iconLibrary": "lucide",
"aliases": {
  "components": "@/components",
  "utils": "@/lib/utils",
  "ui": "@/components/ui",
  "lib": "@/lib",
  "hooks": "@/hooks"
},
"registries": {
  "@aceternity": "https://ui.aceternity.com/registry/{name}.json",
  "@originui": "https://originui.com/r/{name}.json",
  "@cult": "https://cult-ui.com/r/{name}.json",
  "@kibo": "https://www.kibo-ui.com/r/{name}.json",
  "@reui": "https://reui.io/r/{name}.json"
}
